{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b74dfc6905","title":"毛泽东关于粮食征购、配售和管理等几个问题的提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c7a3b2d9b0","index":0,"year":1953,"month":10,"day":12,"articleId":"b74dfc6905"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5db97a3228","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于粮食征购、配售和管理等几个问题的提纲","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"1f8dfd3eff","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"323ccb892a","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"9bccece6b3","type":"paragraph","text":"数目：706亿斤；面大小；一次或多期；征价；标准=控制、评议；运输；征购分开；免购区；指示；物资供应；公债；宣传总路线；少出乱子；明年预购；生产中心；时间安排；配售；暂不登报；统一管理；干部下乡和落后乡。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"96216ad927","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"03df15cbbc","type":"paragraph","text":"统一管理：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"11c2ae9ff4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）由中央公布控制数目，各大区保证完成，负责管理，组织供应；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"07cfa1a06a","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）各区需粮交大区，区省间分配掌握，东北各掌一部；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"7c808a6c17","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）除上外，粮均归中央，包括出口，供给，储备，备大荒，机动等项；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"94b7f71959","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）地方发（生）自己不能克服的困难，中央予以援助；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"9aa58d3a63","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）中央认为需要和可能调出粮食，经慎重考虑决定后，地方应照调，地方小困难应服从全国性的大困难；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"28a6f5cc3b","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）粮价由中央统一规定，中心点及以下的定价原则；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"},{"id":"42087d144b","type":"paragraph","text":"（7）供应标准，全国应大体一致，各地可提意见。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905"}],"page":{"id":"e9ec72f089","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b74dfc6905","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}